               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>An incomplete copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Aruṇācalapurāṇam</title> (text &amp; commentary). Appears to stop at <title xml:lang="ta">Vaccirāṅkatap pāṇṭiyaṉ patavi yaṭainta carukkam</title>, with 451 stanzas. 32 folios without foliation (U2b) to be correctly placed in U2a. The higher extant foliation is 229 and there are only 218 folios (U2a + U2b).</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (March 2023).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p></summary>
                  
